summary: An ordinance authorizing the execution of an agreement between the City and the Port of Seattle, relating to the protection of utilities, right of access for maintenance or construction purposes, and financial responsibility for maintenance and reconstruction of sewers and other utilities in West Hanford Street, between East Marginal Way and the East Waterway, following the vacation of same as proposed by Comptroller's File No. 221857.
committee: Streets and Sewers and City Utilities
